Global File Integrity Monitoring Market Insights
File Integrity Monitoring Market size was valued at USD 1.8 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 3.6 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 9.1% from 2024 to 2030.

File Integrity Monitoring Market Overview
The global File Integrity Monitoring (FIM) market is valued at USD 1.3 billion in 2025 and is projected to grow significantly over the next several years, driven by rising security concerns among businesses across various industries. The market is expected to experience substantial growth due to the increasing need for data protection and compliance regulations. The integration of advanced machine learning algorithms and automation tools has also propelled the demand for file integrity monitoring solutions. Moreover, the growing frequency of cyberattacks and the need for real-time monitoring of critical systems and data is expected to fuel the market’s expansion during the forecast period.

